	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Mar 22nd 1:18 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Is 200 intel really more important than having 200 charisma to an Enchanter?<br>What does charisma affect, other than charming and prices with merchants?<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
